name: VEGAS FORGOTTEN - [HOLLYWOOD PIXELATIONS]
description: Purple bruises a pink sunset as she drives out of town. She has had enough of the plastic promises of Digital Vegas and needs the forgotten part of town. Black analogue signs threaten the skyline and she pixelates them with one look. She is ready to drive back to the Hills for a different form of digital distraction... This is part of a series of dysfunctional digital paintings that I have made about distorted lives in Hollywood called "Hollywood Pixelations".
